{
  "id": 5110223547269120,
  "name": "WebGPU: Texture component swizzle",
  "summary": "Functionality added to the WebGPU spec after its first shipment in a browser.\n\nAllows GPUTextureViews to rearrange or replace the color components from texture's red/green/blue/alpha channels when accessed by a shader.",
